    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
    <h3>How do I use the pitch detection?</h3>
    <p>Allow microphone access when prompted, then play your clarinet. Aimelo will show real-time pitch feedback.</p>
    
    <h3>How do I use the posture detection?</h3>
    <p>Allow camera access when prompted, then position yourself in view while playing.</p>
    
    <h3>How do I track my progress?</h3>
    <p>Your practice sessions are automatically saved. View your calendar and statistics in the Progress tab.</p>
    
